  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Rebecca loses contact with her girlfriend Leanna during a late-night call, fear drives her to investigate. She heads to the Hemisfair Health Clinic, where Leanna was last heard from, only to discover she’s vanished without a trace. As she digs deeper, she crosses paths with unsettling individuals whose actions raise more questions than answers. What begins as a desperate search for Leanna spirals into a harrowing journey to uncover the truth.<br><br><i><strong>Experience this gripping, story-driven third-person adventure where narrative takes center stage.</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ef7075ab867c45769a75ac2bc285c4be.poster.avif?t=1745014775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ef7075ab867c45769a75ac2bc285c4be.webm?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ef7075ab867c45769a75ac2bc285c4be.mp4?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>Investigate the Clinic During the Dead of Night: Embark on a tense late-night exploration of the Hemisfair Health Clinic to uncover the mystery behind Leanna’s disappearance.</strong></i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/16275958bbd24887470cf55451e6d4b6.poster.avif?t=1745014775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/16275958bbd24887470cf55451e6d4b6.webm?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/16275958bbd24887470cf55451e6d4b6.mp4?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i><strong></strong></i> <i><strong>Uncover secrets, and face tense encounters: Stay on your toes during high-stakes situations where your reactions can mean the difference between life and death.</strong></i>    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/53c19f379ef76b768f1426f82b70cde2.poster.avif?t=1745014775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/53c19f379ef76b768f1426f82b70cde2.webm?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/53c19f379ef76b768f1426f82b70cde2.mp4?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i><br>Live the Story in San Antonio: Become part of the narrative as you explore San Antonio, TX, through the eyes of its characters and their challenges</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/11cab10f414806836b935810b123554f.poster.avif?t=1745014775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/11cab10f414806836b935810b123554f.webm?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/11cab10f414806836b935810b123554f.mp4?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><i>Cinematic Storytelling: Engage with immersive cutscene narratives designed to pull you deeper into the story and connect you to the characters' journeys.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ce3adef13a640a8becb11d9af92dbd26.poster.avif?t=1745014775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ce3adef13a640a8becb11d9af92dbd26.webm?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3356570/extras/ce3adef13a640a8becb11d9af92dbd26.mp4?t=1745014775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><i>Checkpoint-Based Saving: The game automatically saves progress at key checkpoints, ensuring a smooth and immersive gameplay experience.</i> </p>",
